name: Samuel Theodore ROSS, Petitioner v. Honorable Carolyn CARLUCCIO, Judge, Montgomery County, Court of Common Pleas, Respondent

parties: Samuel Theodore ROSS, Petitioner v. Honorable Carolyn CARLUCCIO, Judge, Montgomery County, Court of Common Pleas, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of June, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED, and the Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

Samuel Theodore ROSS, Petitioner v. Honorable Carolyn CARLUCCIO, Judge, Montgomery County, Court of Common Pleas, Respondent.

June 29, 2015.
